1
00:00:04,250 --> 00:00:05,550
Charge, Haemeus !

2
00:00:09,825 --> 00:00:11,000
Ne panique pas, Lumi !

3
00:00:11,100 --> 00:00:12,350
Tu te souviens de ton entraînement ?

4
00:00:12,850 --> 00:00:13,950
Je suis à tes côtés.

5
00:00:14,525 --> 00:00:15,475
Prête...

6
00:00:16,025 --> 00:00:16,775
Maintenant !

7
00:00:16,850 --> 00:00:17,625
Saute !

8
00:00:18,950 --> 00:00:19,775
Attaque !

9
00:00:21,325 --> 00:00:22,400
Arrête-la !

10
00:00:44,850 --> 00:00:45,575
Attention !

11
00:00:49,850 --> 00:00:51,400
