19
00:01:30,575 --> 00:01:34,125
Ya-ho !!!

20
00:01:39,300 --> 00:01:40,075
Qu'est-ce que...

21
00:01:57,550 --> 00:01:59,075
Ne t'inquiète pas, Haemus.

22
00:01:59,300 --> 00:02:00,600
On va gagner !

23
00:02:19,700 --> 00:02:20,750
La prophétie...

